data.name: SqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT nID, nAddressID, sJobDesc, dCreated, dJobCreated, sJobNo, nCustID, sPhone, sJobContact, sCounty, nTotalWholesale, sBuildingPermit, sTerms, dDrawing, nMaterialsCharge, nTaxRate, nLaborCharge, sContractSigned, sDisclaimerSigned, sDrawingsSigned, sComplete, sSalesperson, sOtherNotes, dCommPaid, sCommLocked, dCrLimit, dAmtYTD, sInvNotes, lngCommissionStruct FROM dbo.tJob WHERE (nCustID = @NCUSTID) ORDER BY nAddressID, nID

data.name: SqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO dbo.tJob(nAddressID, sJobDesc, dCreated, dJobCreated, sJobNo, nCustID, sPhone, sJobContact, sCounty, nTotalWholesale, sBuildingPermit, sTerms, dDrawing, nMaterialsCharge, nTaxRate, nLaborCharge, sContractSigned, sDisclaimerSigned, sDrawingsSigned, sComplete, sSalesperson, sOtherNotes, dCommPaid, sCommLocked, dCrLimit, dAmtYTD, sInvNotes, lngCommissionStruct) VALUES (@nAddressID, @sJobDesc, @dCreated, @dJobCreated, @sJobNo, @nCustID, @sPhone, @sJobContact, @sCounty, @nTotalWholesale, @sBuildingPermit, @sTerms, @dDrawing, @nMaterialsCharge, @nTaxRate, @nLaborCharge, @sContractSigned, @sDisclaimerSigned, @sDrawingsSigned, @sComplete, @sSalesperson, @sOtherNotes, @dCommPaid, @sCommLocked, @dCrLimit, @dAmtYTD, @sInvNotes, @lngCommissionStruct); SELECT nID, nAddressID, sJobDesc, dCreated, dJobCreated, sJobNo, nCustID, sPhone, sJobContact, sCounty, nTotalWholesale, sBuildingPermit, sTerms, dDrawing, nMaterialsCharge, nTaxRate, nLaborCharge, sContractSigned, sDisclaimerSigned, sDrawingsSigned, sComplete, sSalesperson, sOtherNotes, dCommPaid, sCommLocked, dCrLimit, dAmtYTD, sInvNotes, lngCommissionStruct FROM dbo.tJob WHERE (nID = @@IDENTITY)

data.name: SqlDeleteCommand1.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM dbo.tJob WHERE (nID = @Original_nID) AND (dAmtYTD = @Original_dAmtYTD) AND (dCommPaid = @Original_dCommPaid OR @Original_dCommPaid IS NULL AND dCommPaid IS NULL) AND (dCrLimit = @Original_dCrLimit) AND (dCreated = @Original_dCreated OR @Original_dCreated IS NULL AND dCreated IS NULL) AND (dDrawing = @Original_dDrawing) AND (dJobCreated = @Original_dJobCreated OR @Original_dJobCreated IS NULL AND dJobCreated IS NULL) AND (lngCommissionStruct = @Original_lngCommissionStruct) AND (nAddressID = @Original_nAddressID) AND (nCustID = @Original_nCustID) AND (nLaborCharge = @Original_nLaborCharge) AND (nMaterialsCharge = @Original_nMaterialsCharge) AND (nTaxRate = @Original_nTaxRate) AND (nTotalWholesale = @Original_nTotalWholesale) AND (sBuildingPermit = @Original_sBuildingPermit) AND (sCommLocked = @Original_sCommLocked) AND (sComplete = @Original_sComplete) AND (sContractSigned = @Original_sContractSigned) AND (sCounty = @Original_sCounty) AND (sDisclaimerSigned = @Original_sDisclaimerSigned) AND (sDrawingsSigned = @Original_sDrawingsSigned) AND (sInvNotes = @Original_sInvNotes) AND (sJobContact = @Original_sJobContact) AND (sJobDesc = @Original_sJobDesc) AND (sJobNo = @Original_sJobNo) AND (sOtherNotes = @Original_sOtherNotes) AND (sPhone = @Original_sPhone) AND (sSalesperson = @Original_sSalesperson) AND (sTerms = @Original_sTerms)

data.name: SqlSelectCommand2.CommandText
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT dbo.tAddress.nID, dbo.tAddress.sAddress1, dbo.tAddress.sAddress2, dbo.tAddress.sCity, dbo.tAddress.sState, dbo.tAddress.sCounty, dbo.tAddress.sZip, dbo.tAddress.sLocCode FROM dbo.tAddress INNER JOIN dbo.tJob ON dbo.tAddress.nID = dbo.tJob.nAddressID WHERE (dbo.tJob.nCustID = @NCUSTID) ORDER BY dbo.tAddress.sLocCode
